  mTrueTypeFont: {fileID: 12800000, guid: 334bac67b27041b4a9531adc898105bc, type: 3}
  mFont: {fileID: 0}
  mText: "1. Each player has 4 tokens, whoever gets all 4 tokens to the Home/finishes
    first, he/she is the Winner! Also the game can continue to crown a 2nd winner.
    \n2. Special rules for Arrow mode:\n      # If your token lands on the tail of
    arrow, then it will be moved to head of the arrow and You get another Dice roll
    chance.\n3. The player gets another turn to roll the dice when they\n\tA. Land
    token on tail of arrow\n\tB. Roll 6\n\tC. Get into the Home/cross finish line.\n\tD.
    Captures opponent token\n \n4. A token can be only move out of its Yard if Player
    rolls 6.\n5. Star on the path is 'safe place' for tokens irrespective to its
    color.\n6. If A player gets 3 times 6 continuously (without Landing on Arrow
    tail, Capturing opponent token or finishing a token in between these 3 sixes)
    then the 3rd 6 will be skipped along with their turn."
