  mTrueTypeFont: {fileID: 12800000, guid: 334bac67b27041b4a9531adc898105bc, type: 3}
  mFont: {fileID: 0}
  mText: "1. Whoever gets ONE token to the Home/finishes first, he/she is the Winner!
    Also the game can continue to crown a 2nd winner. \n2. Special rules for Quick
    mode: \n      # Plyer needs to Capture at least ONE token of your opponent to
    clear your path of Home/finish. Otherwise, your token will be kept walking on
    path BUT NEVER get into the Home/finish. \n3. The player gets another turn to
    roll the dice as when they \n    A. Captures opponent token \n\tB. Roll 6 \n   
    C. Get into the Home/cross finish line.\n\tD. Captures opponent token\n \n4.
    A token can be only move out of its Yard if Player rolls 6.\n5. Star on the path
    is 'safe place' for tokens irrespective to its color.\n6. If A player gets 3
    times 6 continuously (without Capturing opponent token or finishing a token in
    between these 3 sixes) then the 3rd 6 will be skipped along with their turn.\n"
