  mText: "1. Each player has 4 tokens, whoever gets all 4 tokens to the Home/finishes
    first, he/she is the Winner! Also the game can continue to crown a 2nd winner.
    \n2. A token can be only move out of Yard if Player rolls 6. \n3. The player
    gets another turn to roll the dice when they \n\tA. Roll 6 \n\tB. Get into Home/cross
    finish line. \n\tC. Captures opponent token \n4. Star on the path is 'safe place'
    for tokens irrespective to its color.\n5. If A player gets 3 times 6 continuously
    (without Capturing opponent token or finishing a token in between these 3 sixes)
    then the 3rd 6 will be skipped along with their turn."
